added.title: The People of the Deep
added.description: Iyanu, Biyi and Sewa face the Corrupt Divine Beast Ekun and the vicious People of the Deep. Meanwhile, in Elu, Workers' District citizens demand justice from Oba Adeyinka and Chancellor Nuro's oppressive regime.

added.title: The Source Part II
added.description: Iyanu reaches The Source and faces a devastating choice about her destiny. As Elu teeters on the brink of destruction from the Corrupt, Iyanu's allies fight a final battle against Chancellor Nuro and the Fallen One.

added.title: The Pink Painter Strikes Again
added.description: They're baaaaack! All 16 Campers from Season One return for more spills, thrills and dramaaaaa! And a very special guest arrives on the island to really mess things up. Hope everyone packed an extra pair of pants!

added.title: Taking it to the Rim Reaper
added.description: Things get wet, wild and gross when the Campers play waterslide basketball!

added.title: You Poor Saps
added.description: Tensions run high in this week's challenge when the Campers find themselves in a sticky situation.

added.title: Choosin' For a Bruisin'
added.description: Our campers get tested on how well they know each other. Correct answers could win them immunity, but incorrect answers drop them into a pool of hungry wolverines.

added.title: The Wheel of Vomit
added.description: Chef finally gets to show off his fancy culinary skills in an eating challenge where each dish is a tastebud's nightmare. The last camper still eating wins immunity. The rest are all up for elimination.

added.title: Paddle Field Earth
added.description: Today's challenge involves canoeing, hiking and mountain climbing. It's just like normal summer camp!! Except that you canoe over a waterfall, hike through a geyser field and climb a mountain that's actually the world's biggest beehive. It's nothing like summer camp.

added.title: The Truth, The Pole Truth and Nothing But the Truth
added.description: If spending the day balancing on a pole under the direct sun with no food in your tummy sounds like a fun time you are going to love today's challenge.

added.title: Tortoise Rigamortis
added.description: With just 5 campers remaining things are getting tense. So today is just about having fun taking selfies with wild animals. Everyone had their rabies shot?

added.title: Caved by the Bell
added.description: The final 4 get must wander through a dark and spooky cave hunting for coins. The challenge only gets worse when they discover that something is also hunting them.

added.title: Magma Cum Laude
added.description: This is it! Today one of the 3 remaining campers will become a millionaire. The only thing standing in their way is 2 other campers, a forest, some lava, some violent goats, a mountain, and vomit. Other than that, pretty easy.

added.title: Braces
added.description: When the Bears go to the dentist, Panda gets braces. But, Panda finds out his braces grant him super abilities and the power goes to his head.

added.title: Christmas Movies
added.description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

added.title: Imaginary Friend
added.description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

added.title: The Mall
added.description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

added.title: Tunnels
added.description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

added.title: Ramen
added.description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

added.title: The Gym
added.description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

added.title: Bubble
added.description: Panda becomes a germophobe and decides to live the rest of his life in a bubble.

added.title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
added.description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

added.title: Fire!
added.description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

added.title: Midnight Quittance
added.description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

added.title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
added.description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

added.title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
added.description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

added.title: Spell Crushers
added.description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

added.title: The Library
added.description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.
